This Java program generates an inverted right-angled triangle pattern of asterisks (*). The pattern size is determined by the user input, and the code utilizes nested loops to efficiently generate the pattern.

PATTERN:

*****
****
***
**
*

PROGRAMM:



class HelloWorld {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        int n=5;
        for(int i=n;i>=1;i--){
            for(int j=1;j<=i;j++){
                System.out.print("*");
            }
            System.out.println();
        }
    }
}
